  <description><![CDATA[<p>From its sunny location above the resort’s centre, the small and charming Alpine style Garni Barbara is truly a home from home! It is beautifully furnished throughout and offers high quality accommodation and excellent service. It is ideally located next to the ski slopes, and only 6 minutes walk (600m) to the resort centre. Facilities include cosy wood-panelled lounge and bar with open fire, where breakfast is served. A mini spa is on hand with sauna, steam room and relaxation area to help you rejuvenate after a day's hard skiing. Dinner is served at their sister property the Sporthotel Arabba which is a 500m downhill walk away.</p>]]></description>
